==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Girlish
<hw>Girl"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like, or characteristic of, a
girl; of or pertaining to girlhood; innocent; artless; immature; weak;
<as>as, <ex>girlish</ex> ways; <ex>girlish</ex> grief.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Girl"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Girl"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Girlond</ent>⟦br⟧
